6.html#section-3.2.2\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI.DomainName","kind":"def","line":172,"name":"Std.Http.URI.DomainName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/URI/Basic.lean#L172-L180"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI.IsValidDomainName\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsValidDomainName</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Proposition that asserts `s` is a valid dot-separated domain name.\nEach label must satisfy `IsValidDomainLabel`, and the full name must be at most 255 characters.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI.IsValidDomainName","kind":"def","line":164,"name":"Std.Http.URI.IsValidDomainName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/URI/Basic.lean#L164-L170"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI.isValidDomainLabel\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">isValidDomainLabel</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc